OL,3,CPublic spending 'trade-offs' needed to
OL,4,Cmeet defence pledge, Cameron accepts
OL,6,FLord Cameron has acknowledged that
OL,7,Fpublic spending "trade-offs" will be
OL,8,Fneeded to meet the Government's pledge
OL,9,Fto increase the defence budget, after
OL,10,FPrime Minister Rishi Sunak declined to
OL,11,Frule out cuts beyond the civil service.
OL,13,FThe Foreign Secretary said the
OL,14,Fannouncement to raise spending to 2.5%
OL,15,Fof GDP by 2030 was a "very clear
OL,16,Fdemonstration" of the Conservative
OL,17,FGovernment's priorities.
