OL,3,CPublic spending 'trade-offs' needed to
OL,4,Cmeet defence pledge, Cameron accepts
OL,6,FMr Sunak says it will be funded by
OL,7,Fcutting 72,000 civil service jobs, but
OL,8,Feconomists have said the commitment
OL,9,Fwill hit other areas as well.
OL,11,FDuring a five-day visit to Central
OL,12,FAsia, Lord Cameron said the commitment
OL,13,Fwas "necessary" to protect national
OL,14,Fsecurity as "the first priority of
OL,15,Fgovernment".
