OL,6,FIn an election year, the Tories hope
OL,7,Fthe Prime Minister's commitment will
OL,8,Fbe a key dividing line with Labour,
OL,9,Fwhich has also said it will raise the
OL,10,Fbudget to 2.5%, only when economic
OL,11,Fconditions allow.
OL,13,FThe 2030 pledge was previously made by
OL,14,FBoris Johnson in 2022 following
OL,15,FRussia's invasion of Ukraine.
