OL,6,FAsked how Mr Sunak's announcement
OL,7,Fdiffered from the former prime
OL,8,Fminister's promise to raise defence
OL,9,Fspending to 2.5%, the Foreign
OL,10,FSecretary said: "There's a great
OL,11,Fdifference between making a pledge and
OL,12,Factually having a plan to achieve a
OL,13,Fpledge."
