OL,6,FHe said the plan is "fully funded"
OL,7,Fwith a reduction in the civil service
OL,8,Fheadcount and an uplift in research
OL,9,Fand development spending, but added
OL,10,Fthat "we are making a choice to
OL,11,Fprioritise defence".
OL,13,FPressed to rule out further cuts, the
OL,14,FPrime Minister said: "We have record
OL,15,Finvestment in our public services,
OL,16,Fincluding the NHS ` that's not going
OL,17,Fto change, it's going to continue.
