OL,3,CPublic spending 'trade-offs' needed to
OL,4,Cmeet defence pledge, Cameron accepts
OL,6,FAfter Mr Sunak's announcement on
OL,7,FTuesday, the UK Government has said it
OL,8,Fwants that benchmark to increase to
OL,9,F2.5%, which would add #140 billion to
OL,10,Fthe Nato budget if met by all 32
OL,11,Fmembers.
OL,13,FThe Institute for Fiscal Studies (IFS)
OL,14,Fhas said unprotected areas of public
OL,15,Fspending will now face cuts of about
OL,16,F4% a year after 2025 to help meet the
OL,17,Fdefence commitment.
