OL,6,FDowning Street said the plan would
OL,7,Fcost #4.5 billion in 2028/29, of which
OL,8,F#2.9 billion would come from savings
OL,9,Fbecause of the reduction in the size
OL,10,Fof the civil service, with #1.6
OL,11,Fbillion coming from the research and
OL,12,Fdevelopment budget.
OL,14,FNo 10 would not give any further
OL,15,Fdetails of where jobs would be lost or
OL,16,Fwhether the reduction in headcount
OL,17,Fcould be achieved through natural
OL,18,Fwastage or if it would require
OL,19,Fredundancies.
