OL,6,FDetails will be set out at a future
OL,7,Fspending review, a spokeswoman said.
OL,9,FLabour has said the Tories "have shown
OL,10,Ftime and time again that they cannot
OL,11,Fbe trusted".
OL,13,FShadow defence secretary John Healey
OL,14,Fsaid that "since 2010, the
OL,15,FConservatives have wasted more than
OL,16,F#15 billion mismanaging defence
OL,17,Fprocurement, shrunk the army to its
OL,18,Fsmallest size since Napoleon, missed
OL,19,Ftheir recruitment targets every year,
OL,20,Fand allowed morale to fall to record
OL,21,Flows".
